vote.title: An ordinance abandoning a portion of an alley to SCP/OI Good Latimer OZ Owner, LLC, the abutting owner, containing approximately 5,840 square feet of land, located near the intersection of Good Latimer Expressway and Louise Avenue; and authorizing the quitclaim - Revenue: General Capital Reserve Fund ($109,064.00) General Fund ($20,000.00), plus the $20.00 ordinance publication fee
